      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 8 Business Day article on daily performance of stock market</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article in Business Day on Saturday about the daily performance of the stock market misstated the last time the Nasdaq composite index closed above 4,000 points. It was in June, not April.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
